====Spelling note====
The spelling "[[theatre]]" is the main spelling in Commonwealth English, with "[[theater]]" being rare.  In United States English, "[[Theatre]]" mainly only occurs in proper nouns, albeit not universally even then.

In United States English, "[[theatre]]" is most often used to denote the dramatic arts, whereas "[[theater]]" denotes a physical structure to house performances.

